snippet.textDisplay:
Wow! I'm stunned and mesmerized. 💯
This is what coke studio is supposed to offer to its audience. Something which is peaceful. 

Zeb Bangash has an absolute angelic voice. Got me in tears with her first alaap and after that it went directly into the realms of serenity and peace which was again beautifully depicted in the videography as well.

As a bold and honest critic of the more Gen-Z-oriented CS lately (post-Xulfi oc) I had lost my interest in the show but I must say after O yaara and this song, I am ready to look forward to the next season. 👍

Once again, a masterpiece production. 🙌
